# Master Blueprint: G Arginia E-Commerce Startup

This document outlines the technical requirements and "Master Prompts" to replicate the high-end performance, SEO, and design quality of the **Akram Coaching** project for your new e-commerce brand.

---

## 🏗️ The "Technical DNA" (Tech Stack)
To match the current site's performance, the new project **must** use:
- **Core**: React 19 + Vite 6 (for near-instant load times).
- **Style**: Tailwind CSS 4 + `motion/react` (Framer Motion) + GSAP (for "artboard" animations).
- **3D**: Three.js + React Three Fiber (for that premium interactive feel).
- **AI**: Google Gemini API (for an intelligent shopping assistant).
- **Commerce**: Chargily (local DZD) + PayPal (International) + Supabase (for database/admin).

---

## 📝 Sequence of Master Prompts (with UI/UX Pro Max)

Copy and paste these prompts in order. These are optimized to use the **UI/UX Pro Max** design intelligence already present in this environment.

### 🧠 Prompt 0: Organize Thoughts (Preparation)
> "Before we start, let's organize our thoughts. Analyze the technical DNA of the current 'Akram Coaching' project (Vite 6, React 19, Three.js, GSAP). We are going to build a new e-commerce startup, **G Arginia**, that inherits this exact performance and SEO structure but with a unique 'Artboard' design. Confirm you have access to the `ui-ux-pro-max` skill and prepare to use it for all design decisions."

### Phase 1: The Core Foundation
> "Initialize a new high-end e-commerce project for the brand 'G Arginia' using **React 19, Vite 6, and Tailwind CSS 4**. The design should follow a unique 'Artboard' aesthetic. Set up a professional file structure that includes folders for `components/3d`, `pages`, `lib`, and `i18n`. Ensure the [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Laylo/Downloads/akram-coaching-main/akram-coaching-main/index.html) is pre-configured with SEO meta tags, Open Graph data, and JSON-LD structured data for a 'LocalBusiness' and 'Store'."

### Phase 2: Design & Motion System
> "Implement a 'Glassmorphism' design system. Create a global [index.css](file:///c:/Users/Laylo/Downloads/akram-coaching-main/akram-coaching-main/src/index.css) with custom red/dark gradients and a typography system using premium fonts (like Inter or Outfit). Use **GSAP** and **motion/react** to create a 'Master Layout' where page transitions feel like an artboard sliding in. Every button must have a spring-based hover animation and a subtle 'glow' effect."

### Phase 3: High-End Features (3D & AI)
> "Integrate **Three.js** via React Three Fiber to create a subtle, interactive 3D background (like a nebula or floating brand elements). Then, create an **AI Shopping Assistant** component powered by the **Google Gemini API**. The assistant should be able to answer product questions and guide users through the catalog, following the 'AKBOT' pattern from the coaching project."

### Phase 4: E-Commerce & Analytics
> "Set up the e-commerce logic. Integrate **Chargily Pay** for the Algerian market and **PayPal** for international sales. Implement a **Supabase** backend to track site visits and store product data. Create a professional 'Product Intake' flow that collects user information before checkout, similar to the coaching client intake form. Ensure all product cards have 'Add to Cart' animations using GSAP."

